# Common Rules — Limerence Workspace

## Comments — preserve, don't delete

When editing code, preserving existing documentation has higher priority than cleanup.

- Keep `@see docs/...` links; migrate when moving code
- Keep «why» comments and JSDoc
- Gameplay logic → update spec in `docs/specs/` + `@see` in code

## Spec before code

**Source of truth:** `docs/specs/` and `docs/monetization/`.

1. Read relevant spec before coding
2. Update spec if behavior changes
3. Implement with `@see docs/specs/...`
4. Remove code paths not in spec

